{"tid":2268192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7個月「零客」 高鐵虧損料公帑包底 預料以億元計","createTime":"2020-11-02T15:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T15:55:01.000Z","uid":240918,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"938c91f21da24fc0c4eded86c5d2fa8d144e7859","tid":2268192,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mjqQRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mjqQRu.jpg&h=0aeaa724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即將迎來通車兩周年的高鐵香港段，受本港爆發疫情影響，自今年1月30日起暫停營運，重開無期，令高鐵營運出現嚴重虧損。運輸及房屋局首次證實，由於高鐵至今停駛7個月，初步估計由政府全資擁有的九鐵公司，須按高鐵「乘客量上下限機制」承擔部分風險；即意味政府需要「包底」補貼港鐵營運高鐵的虧蝕。有立法會議員估計，政府的補貼開支以億元計，停運愈久，補貼公帑開支愈高，要求政府交代高鐵財務情况。【明報專訊】"},{"pid":"580fc1df342526199c8faa8b1575991820ddb512","tid":2268192,"uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:10:51.000Z","msg":"為本港引入第一宗武漢肺炎<br />\n已經完成歷史任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ef4eb08d6c58cf94bfdd83551986f5612997ea","tid":2268192,"uid":99828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"梁愛詩：高鐵無一地兩檢就要炸毀車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時幾時???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif